<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ride Confirmation Email - Amorous</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }

        table {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #004225;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .ride-details {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .ride-details td {
            padding: 10px 5px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .ride-details strong {
            color: #333333;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #004225;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888888;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        /* Responsive styling */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content, .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .ride-details td {
                padding: 8px 0;
            }

            .button {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td class="header">
                    Ride Confirmation - Amorous
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
                    <p>Thank you for confirming your ride with Amorous! Your ride has been successfully booked.
                        Below are the details of your upcoming ride:</p>

                    <table class="ride-details" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Car Name:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= car_name %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Car Type:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= car_type %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Reservation Number:</strong></td>
                            <td>#<%= reservation_number %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Pick-up Location:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= pickupLocation %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Drop-off Location:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= dropoffLocation %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Ride Duration:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= duration %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <!-- <tr>
                            <td><strong>Pickup Date & Time:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= pickupDateAndTime %></td>
                        </tr> -->
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Pickup Date & Time:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= new Date(pickupDateAndTime).toLocaleString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric', hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: true }) %></td>
                        </tr>
                        
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Return Ride:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= return_ride %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <!-- <tr>
                            <td><strong>Return Date & Time:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= return_pickup_date_time %></td>
                        </tr> -->
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Return Date & Time:</strong></td>
                            <td><%= new Date(return_pickup_date_time).toLocaleString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric', hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: true }) %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Total Amount:</strong></td>
                            <td>$<%= total_amount %></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    <div class="button-container">
                        <a href="<%= manageRideUrl %>" class="button">Manage Your Ride</a>
                    </div>

                    <p>We look forward to providing you with a comfortable and safe ride.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    &copy; 2024 Amorous. All rights reserved.
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
